  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13102978/christmas-decoration.jpg" alt="ChristmasSkiHol" data-udi="umb://media/82667fa7299349fdbcf6f765c569458a" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Treat yourself to a ski holiday this Christmas. Snow-covered slopes, glittering lights and roaring fires make any winter stay at a ski resort an unforgettable experience. </p>
<p>One of the many reasons you'll love skiing at Christmas is that there are so many special touches throughout the resort.</p>
<p>Markets, lights and wonderful scenery all capture an extra special atmosphere. From luxurious ski-in ski-out properties, to cosy chalets with a log fire, our collection of ski accommodation is sure to tick all your boxes.</p>
<p>Christmas is extremely popular and the best resorts sell out quickly so we advise that you book as early as possible, especially if you're looking for a <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/accommodation-options/chalets">catered ski chalet</a> over Christmas. </p>
<p>Experience the ultimate white Christmas</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/794f2adfc92b4f9fa39c120e0b35a3bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/794f2adfc92b4f9fa39c120e0b35a3bb}" title="December" class="c-btn">View December ski deals</a></p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13090993/christmas-trees-lights-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/9770efdc5def423ba0d5914a4012148a" /></p>
<h3>Christmas 2024 Holidays</h3>
<p>Choose a December ski holiday and experience the magic of Christmas. With snow-covered slopes, roaring log fires and gorgeous views, December ski holidays bring you everything you need for a magical time on and off the slopes. </p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/960b373c69434d9ea227fe18b1770f8d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/960b373c69434d9ea227fe18b1770f8d}" title="Christmas Ski Holidays" class="c-btn">View Christmas ski holidays</a></div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13090994/ski-resort-fireworks-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/6f772af0e7124a64a19f1b84027be813" /></p>
<h3>New Year 2024 Holidays</h3>
<p>Enjoy New Year's Eve on the slopes and welcome in 2025 on a fresh set of snowy slopes. There's not much to compare to the buzz of skiing on New Year's Day and celebrating New Year's Eve in the mountains – it's a one-of-a-kind experience.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/aea32888d03e4f5499689d39abf2ea36" href="/{localLink:umb://document/aea32888d03e4f5499689d39abf2ea36}" title="New Year Ski Holidays" class="c-btn">View New Year ski holidays</a></div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13090995/tignes-snow-view-of-town-314x194.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/7222d2281ce34fbd925b8775565e7278" /></p>
<h3>December 2024 Holidays</h3>
<p>Make your December holiday plans now. With no crowds and snow-heavy slopes, a December ski holiday is the ideal time to hit the powder. You can enjoy the winter wonderland of snow, glistening sunshine, and fresh mountain air. </p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/794f2adfc92b4f9fa39c120e0b35a3bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/794f2adfc92b4f9fa39c120e0b35a3bb}" title="December Ski Deals" class="c-btn">View December ski holidays</a></div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2><span>Best Christmas skiing accommodation</span></h2>
<p><span>Discover our favourite hotels, perfect for a Christmas ski holiday. </span></p>
<div id="top" class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h4 style="color: #003155; text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/f74ea0f740eb408382ae98f5f1082ece" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f74ea0f740eb408382ae98f5f1082ece}?departureDate=04%2F05%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29112&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000" title="Hotel Tirolerhof" data-anchor="?departureDate=04%2F05%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29112&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000">Hotel Salzburgerhof</a></h4>
<p style="color: #003155;"><img style="width: 500px; height: 268.49642004773267px;" src="/media/13083274/swimming-pool-_-wellness-area-at-night-zell-am-see-austria-min.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="HotelSalz" data-udi="umb://media/a22267987c954bbf98cdd8fd6fcbea2a" /></p>
<p>One of Zell am See’s leading hotels, Hotel Salzburgerhof offers 5* service, award winning food and an amazing wellness / spa area.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1}" class="c-btn">Zell am See - Austria</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h4 style="color: #003155; text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/186ae4f2a99c4d6589e4e5f132e5b3d7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/186ae4f2a99c4d6589e4e5f132e5b3d7}?departureDate=15%2F06%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29112&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000" title="Hotel Alpenaussicht" data-anchor="?departureDate=15%2F06%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29112&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000">Hotel Alpenaussicht</a></h4>
<p style="color: #003155;"><img style="width: 500px; height: 268.49642004773267px;" src="/media/13089349/alpenaussicht_exterior_four.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="HotelAlpen" data-udi="umb://media/387d79000fd3423180e5418175c0d96c" /></p>
<p>Known for its incredible views and authentic food, this charming hotel is a short walk from the village center and ski lifts.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a style="text-align: start;" data-udi="umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576}" class="c-btn">Obergurgl - Austria</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h4 style="color: #003155; text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/31c68aa7fc094c5699d32e8cb731f200" href="/{localLink:umb://document/31c68aa7fc094c5699d32e8cb731f200}?departureDate=01%2F05%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29137&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000" title="La Folie Douce Hotel" data-anchor="?departureDate=01%2F05%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29137&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000">La Folie Douce Hotel</a></h4>
<p style="color: #003155;"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13092334/la-folie-douce-chamonix-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/7bd7d81a3110448da0886b28c9d49a48" /></p>
<p>A truly unique hotel with an eclectic style, ski-in/ski-out access, world class apres, spa and wellness facilities and so much more.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a style="text-align: start;" data-udi="umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0}" class="c-btn">Chamonix - France</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h4 style="color: #003155; text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/6d862a7043db4af4bd3aeba9ab6273fc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d862a7043db4af4bd3aeba9ab6273fc}?departureDate=01%2F05%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29137&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000" title="Chalet Les Arolles" data-anchor="?departureDate=01%2F05%2F2022&amp;duration=7&amp;departurePoint=AIRPORT-LGW&amp;adults=2&amp;children=0&amp;brandCode=ING&amp;programCode=GBINB&amp;regionType=29137&amp;id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000">Chalet Les Arolles</a></h4>
<p style="color: #003155; text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13095551/dsc00405.jpg" alt="ChaletLesArolles" data-udi="umb://media/0d3f134673314027a8dcd0157a47437e" /></p>
<p>Ideal for easy access to the slopes, Chalet Les Arolles is just a short walk to the resort centre and the Grande Motte funicular. You can also enjoy the indoor pool and games room.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a style="text-align: start;" data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" class="c-btn">Tignes - France</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/960b373c69434d9ea227fe18b1770f8d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/960b373c69434d9ea227fe18b1770f8d}" class="c-btn">View Christmas ski holidays</a></p>
<p><a href="#top" data-anchor="#top">Back to top of page</a></p>
<h2>Best resorts with a Christmas feel</h2>
<p><span>We’ve hand-picked some of the best snow-sure resorts for the ultimate white Christmas. </span></p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576}" title="Obergurgl">Obergurgl - Austria</a></h2>
<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13092327/obergurgl-400x208.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/a950fd90eec6439f88c82346d5b6bcd9" /></p>
<ul>
<li>The town itself blends a luxury touch with a friendly and relaxed atmosphere and has plenty of Tyrolean traditions to be enjoyed.</li>
<li>Enjoy a cosy Christmas in Obergurgl and make tracks on the snow-covered slopes. Befriend locals and make new friends, before relaxing with a glass of mulled wine in a slope-side bar.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6063ab813f384ab795dc6aa1d337f576}" title="Obergurgl" class="c-btn">View Obergurgl</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes - France</a></h2>
<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13092313/tignes-400x208.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/6104970c22de40819ddaf782c8b8f606" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Whether you want to relax, party or play this Christmas, Tignes ticks all the boxes. Sister resort to Val d'Isère, it brings altitude as well as attitude. With 300km of piste and extensive off-piste, it's a vast winter playground for all levels.</li>
<li>In terms of apres ski, Tignes doesn't disappoint either, with lively bars and restaurants lining the resort's pretty tree-lined streets.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes" class="c-btn">View Tignes</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/f1003f9fd15e4187b02398fa5c12dc50" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f1003f9fd15e4187b02398fa5c12dc50}" title="Saas Fee">Saas Fee - Switzerland</a></h2>
<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13092328/saas-fee-view-400x208.jpg" alt="Saas Fee" data-udi="umb://media/6a8c515d669649008a4c54d89f37fc55" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Christmas in the Alps doesn’t come any more picturesque than Saas-Fee. Not only does it have a pretty car-free village, but plenty of cosy bars for mulled wine. </li>
<li>The resort’s unique snow record, long winter season and high altitude make it a perfect place to go skiing over Christmas.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/f1003f9fd15e4187b02398fa5c12dc50" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f1003f9fd15e4187b02398fa5c12dc50}" title="Saas Fee" class="c-btn">View Saas Fee</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1}" title="Zell am See">Zel am See - Austria</a></h2>
<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13092329/zel-am-see-children-skiing-400x208.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/9dee3afc78fc4c17b5771aed8b0f1515" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Christmas in Zell am See is like falling into a beautiful snow globe of old-world tradition and warmth, a time when the Austrian spirit of Gemütlichkeit (customary good cheer or festivity) becomes even more tangible.</li>
<li>The market square and surrounding streets are filled with festive aromas, and Christmas decorations and lights create a magical yuletide atmosphere.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1}" title="Zell am See" class="c-btn">View Zell am See</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;"></div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix - France</a></h2>
<p><img style="width: 400px; height: 208px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13092315/chamonix-400x208.jpg?width=400&amp;height=208" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/0868fb6d462f483d883b3de2acd9b88e" /></p>
<ul>
<li>The atmosphere in Chamonix is simply electric at Christmas, as it is in many other French ski resorts. Perfect for Christmas skiing, the snow in Chamonix is usually great in late December thanks to vast amounts of the ski area having an altitude over 2,000m.</li>
<li>With Christmas lights adorning historical buildings that date back over a century, Santa appearing from the roof of Chamonix’s taller buildings and cheeses galore, Chamonix has it all covered.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0}" title="Chamonix" class="c-btn">View Chamonix</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;"></div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas">Yllas - Lapland</a></h2>
<p><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13092330/yllas-snowy-trees-sunrise-400x208.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/2f10f26fbd8246d5bf4d5f0d6c397104" /></p>
<ul>
<li>Log cabins and walking around the snow-white streets decked out in lights, will make you feel as though you’ve walked into a scene from a Christmas film!</li>
<li>Ylläs offers everything you could want from a winter holiday and more, plenty of snow-related activities on offer. Whether you’re browsing the shops in the charming village centre, ice-fishing, dog-sledding or skiing, you’re guaranteed an unforgettable Christmas.<span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0}" title="Lapland Holidays" class="c-btn">View Lapland</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
